# Kopia Backup Exclusion Patterns
# These paths will be excluded from backups

# === Mounted Filesystems ===
# rclone mounts (music, etc.)
**/music/**
**/mnt/rclone/**
music/

# === Temporary & Cache Data ===
**/tmp/**
**/temp/**
**/.cache/**
**/cache/**
**/__pycache__/**
**/node_modules/**

# === Build Artifacts ===
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/.next/**

# === Version Control ===
**/.git/**
**/.svn/**

# === Database Transaction Logs ===
**/pg_wal/**
**/pg_log/**
**/mysql-logs/**
**/mysql-bin.*/**

# === Docker Internal ===
**/.docker/**

# === Backup Tool Data ===
10-backup/kopia-cache/
10-backup/kopia-logs/
10-backup/kopia-repository/
10-backup/rclone-config/
